description: Stunning Waterfront Luxury Residence at 22 Liberty Drive Seaport.This beautiful spacious 5D residence features 2 bedrooms,2.5 bathrooms+Den with breathtaking water views of Boston Harbor&City skyline.Large center island,custom high-gloss white lacquer cabinetry state of the art appliances Wolf stove&wall oven,Miele,Subzero,wine chiller.Spacious open concept living/dining room area that leads to the private balcony over looking the beautiful Boston Harbor&City Skyline views.The primary suite features majestic water views,luxurious bathroom with marble soaking tub,glass,enclosed shower,double vanity,2-walk-in closets.2nd en-suite bedroom with exquisite water views,walk-in closet, 2nd closet&full bath.Large Den ideal for home office or guestroom.Direct 2 car tandem parking and storage unit.Amenities include 24 hour concierge/doorman,fitness center,residents lounge with private terrace overlooking the harbor walk.Located to Seaport District's finest restaurants,shops,cafes,shops,Airport.
